&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Recruiting Strategy &amp;amp; Applicant Attraction&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead the campus component of the overall recruiting strategy to attract a strong and diverse pipeline of talent that aligns to program goals.&lt;/li&gt;
