&lt;li&gt;Build external partnerships with diversity, student and industry specific organizations both through on campus contacts and through national conference opportunities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Understand business and competitive landscape to influence &amp;amp; shape future recruiting strategies.&lt;/li&gt;
